$$
$$
\begin{gathered}

\Rightarrow B(T)=\mu_{0} \frac{\lambda}{4 \pi^{2} a} \omega(T)

\end{gathered} \tag{A1-8}

$$



Combining equations A1-5 and A1-8, we have:



$$

\omega(T)=\frac{\frac{\lambda a^{2}}{2 I} B_{0}}{1+\mu_{0} \frac{\lambda^{2} a}{8 \pi I}}

$$

